Cell["\<\
Notice that this is what I have been motivated elsewhere to call a \"blinking\
\" design: the node on which the walker stands changes color with each step. \
\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.531767680651917*^9, 3.531767780022476*^9}}],

